WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
In Browse Products, tap any product you like.

00:03.000 --> 00:05.000
It's listed at the real PKR price — just tap "+ Add".

00:05.000 --> 00:07.000
Opened the full brand page? Come back here and + Add — no paste.

00:07.000 --> 00:09.500
Pick your size and save it.

00:09.500 --> 00:11.500
It's in your order list — with the all-in BDT total.
